Paper Reading Seminar 2012-09-10
=========

We'll introduce two papers within one hour.

 * B. Yao, A. Khosla, and L. Fei-Fei, "Combining randomization and discrimination for fine-grained image categorization," CVPR 2011.
 * Alexe, B., Deselares, T. and Ferrari, V. "Measuring the objectness of image windows," PAMI 2012. 

 Click the folder icon to download the slides.
